 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.4","title":"C.4: Cross-feature integration tests for search-analytics flow","description":"WHAT: Integration tests covering the full bidirectional flow: (1) search → select result → open detail modal → switch to Analytics tab → verify data matches, (2) view analytics chart → select element → drill-down → verify search filters correct, (3) search results show inline analytics badges → verify values match detail modal analytics. WHY: The integration between search and analytics involves multiple state transitions and data queries — integration tests catch issues that unit tests miss (e.g. filter construction producing no results, analytics data not matching between views). HOW: Build on existing cross_workstream_integration.rs pattern (1758 lines, 74 tests). Create test fixtures with known analytics data, then verify roundtrip. KEY FILES: tests/cross_workstream_integration.rs (existing pattern), src/ui/app.rs (test module). ACCEPTANCE: All cross-feature flows have integration test coverage.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T05:59:35.102137227Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T06:01:30.617247176Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.4","depends_on_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T05:59:35.102137227Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.4","depends_on_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T06:01:30.472310070Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.4","depends_on_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T06:01:30.546499106Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.4","depends_on_id":"coding_agent_session_search-3nwtd.3.3","type":"blocks","created